{
  "texts": [
    "This study aimed to investigate the impact of previous programming knowledge on students' AI interaction profiles, the effect of different AI integration interventions on students' performance, and the association between AI interaction profiles and students' performance within each intervention.",
    "Additionally, how these interventions influenced students' AI interaction profiles over time was also examined.",
    "Regarding the analysis of students' prompting behaviors while they were interacting with ChatGPT, five distinct AI interaction profiles were identified as AI-Reliant Code Generators, AI-Reliant Code Generator & Refiners, AI-Assisted Code Refiners, AI-Independent Coders, and AI-Collaborative Coders.",
    "Building on the profiles described, many students tended to use AI for quick and easy assistance across all interventions.",
    "However, a specific group demonstrated a strategy of putting an initial effort to improve their existing code while collaborating with AI to complete certain tasks."
  ]
}